# Domain Spec Sync With Data Model

When changing model structures, update conceptual specs in the same change set.

- Keep `spec/domain/*.puml` diagrams aligned with model semantics.
- Keep `spec/domain/domain-sync-mapping.json` aligned with renamed or re-scoped entities.
- Keep checker docs and scripts aligned when checker behavior changes.
